    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Flavianii </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Omnium virtutum expe<lb break="no" n="2"/>rientissimo viro ingeni<lb break="no" n="3"/>tae mansuetudinis et be<lb break="no" n="4"/>nignitate patientiae pollenti <lb n="5"/>iudiciorum aequissimo mode<lb break="no" n="6"/>ratori antistiti innocentiae <lb n="7"/>Magnio Aspero Flaviano <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> praesi<lb break="no" n="8"/>di provinciae Tripolitanae Lepci<lb break="no" n="9"/>magnenses ob eius amorem in se <lb n="10"/>conlatum et integritatem perpen<lb break="no" n="11"/>sae <note>sic</note> sibi cognitam patrono dig<lb break="no" n="12"/>nissimo famae et gloriae per<lb break="no" n="13"/>petuum testimonium posuerunt
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Interpunktion: Palmette und kleiner Kranz. The inscription is carved over an erased earlier text.</p>
            </div>
